---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the Hypervisor startup sequence.

Every Hypervisor implementation SHALL follow this lifecycle.

Startup SHALL be deterministic.

Service initialization order SHALL be identical across all implementations.

---

# 2. Startup Goals

Startup SHALL ensure:

* configuration validity;
* storage availability;
* deterministic service initialization;
* dependency correctness;
* provider discovery;
* endpoint restoration;
* safe network publication.

The Hypervisor SHALL NOT publish itself before it is fully operational.

---

