---

# 19. Design Invariants

Invariant 1

Configuration is validated before any service construction.

---

Invariant 2

Migrations complete before services start.

---

Invariant 3

Providers never start before Endpoints are restored.

---

Invariant 4

Advertisements are never published before health verification.

---

Invariant 5

External requests are accepted only after entering the Ready state.

---

Invariant 6

Shutdown always occurs in reverse dependency order.
